OL,3,CPolice appeal for help after man
OL,4,Cabsconds from prison
OL,6,FPolice have warned of "potential risk"
OL,7,Fafter appealing for information to
OL,8,Fhelp locate a man who has absconded
OL,9,Ffrom a prison in Monmouthshire.
OL,11,FGwent Police said Liam Wall left HMP
OL,12,FPrescoed on Sunday 14 December.
OL,14,FThe 36 year-old was convicted of drug
OL,15,Foffences at Cardiff Crown Court in
OL,16,FJuly 2017, and been described as being
OL,17,Faround 5 foot 8 inches tall, bald,
OL,18,Fwith brown eyes and a brown beard.
