OL,6,FA spokesperson for the force said: "It
OL,7,Fis believed there may be a potential
OL,8,Frisk due to the fact that he is no
OL,9,Flonger in the custody of the prison
OL,10,Fservice.
OL,12,F"Gwent Police has activated its
OL,13,Foperational plan with the aim of
OL,14,Flocating Wall and the prison is co-
OL,15,Foperating fully with us.
