OL,6,F"Members of the public are advised not
OL,7,Fto approach Wall and to instead call
OL,8,Fpolice if they see him, or have any
OL,9,Finformation, on 101, quoting
OL,10,F2500396403, you can send a direct
OL,11,Fmessage on Facebook or X, or online.
OL,13,F"Alternatively, you can call
OL,14,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,15,F111 or visit www.crimestoppers-uk.org."
